{"tid":2410104,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華成陰謀論「超級傳播者」","createTime":"2021-02-16T10:36:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T10:36:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9dbd8afb329ea6e723a331987ee14f7e6540566d","tid":2410104,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:36:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210216/EY2S7UX44JFEVMFGNXO42CFJMY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210216%2FEY2S7UX44JFEVMFGNXO42CFJMY%2F&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BfsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=b61273a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210216%2FEY2S7UX44JFEVMFGNXO42CFJMY%2F&h=addf4a6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210216/EY2S7UX44JFEVMFGNXO42CFJMY/</a><br />\n<br />\n華成陰謀論「超級傳播者」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RuM7_MH0iHqxX06BOEe8rbfDFLE=/1332x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JLVCO2Y6YZHABMDH5OCKDKETT4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRuM7_MH0iHqxX06BOEe8rbfDFLE%3D%2F1332x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJLVCO2Y6YZHABMDH5OCKDKETT4.jpg&h=1510a70d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■被指最先爆疫的武漢華南海鮮市場仍被當局封鎖。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人趙立堅去年曾在Twitter貼文，聲稱「新冠病毒可能是由美軍帶到中國武漢」，掀起中美有關病毒源頭的罵戰。美聯社的調查報道稱，疫情爆發以來中美俄和伊朗四國一些政治人物及網媒，成為疫情陰謀論等失實資訊的「超級傳播者」，其中中國取代俄羅斯成為假消息的最大來源國。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：世衞專家溯源調查：武漢早現13病毒株  要求提供20萬血液樣本深入研究<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n取代俄成假消息最大來源國<br />\n<br />\n美聯社與華府智庫大西洋理事會旗下的數碼鑒別研究實驗室合作，調查疫情發以。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報道指，趙立堅在Twitter指控美軍「傳播病毒」的11則推文，被以至少54種語言引用逾9.9萬次，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社"}]}